    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know u aren't a doctor but i'm just trying to figure out if it's even a possibility. my doctor is out of the office until monday and i really dont want to have to go to the urgent care for just a headache if i dont have to. is ibuprofen usually considered safe for people on blood thinners or is it like a major thing?",
